"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-24-paris-drug-dealers-say-theyre-ready-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - France has declared itself prepared for the deluge of Olympics visitors - and so have Paris's drug dealers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"the deluge\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics visitors\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 93}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dealers have promised a steady supply of wares, but warned prices may go up and delivery wait times too under the weight of tens of thousands of security forces and heavy demand.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The dealers\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 142}, {\"ngram\": \"a steady supply\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 172}, {\"ngram\": \"wares\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"warned prices\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"tens of thousands\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"security forces\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 295}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy demand\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Parisians renting out their apartments, to a transit system that has boosted its ticket prices, everyone is looking to make a buck during the Games - and that includes the underworld.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"their apartments\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"a transit system\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"its ticket prices\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"a buck\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the underworld\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are always ready in this business,\\\" a Parisian dealer told AFP, echoing French leader Emmanuel Macron's judgment this week that his nation is all set for the Games.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9980425246882292, \"rank\": 0.001961314536318221, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.654306833465414, \"rank\": 0.34110567003927295, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this business\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"a Parisian dealer\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"his nation\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will always be somebody ready, that's how it is when there is money to be made,\\\" said the dealer, on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"the dealer\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"condition\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymity\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 45,000 security forces policing the streets, experts expect delivery services will see a bump in clients seeking to avoid getting busted.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"up to 45,000 security forces\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery services\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"a bump\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, France has already had a boom in messaging app and social media-driven drug deliveries since pandemic lockdowns pushed the trade off the street and onto smartphone screens.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"a boom\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"app\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"social media-driven drug deliveries\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"pandemic lockdowns\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"the trade\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"smartphone screens\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, the country has voiced increasing alarm over a flourishing drug trade and deadly violence between rival gangs.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"increasing alarm\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"a flourishing drug trade\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"deadly violence\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"rival gangs\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a kind of Uberisation of drug trafficking, with the development of digital offerings on applications like Telegram, or promotional deals,\\\" said criminal attorney Adrien Gabeaud.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.65518574381941e-21, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}, {\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"score\": 0.999999999794909, \"rank\": 1.0010462649987534e-10, \"text\": \"Adrien\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kind\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"Uberisation\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"drug trafficking\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"digital offerings\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"applications\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"promotional deals\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the run-up to the Games, dealers have been updating their clients on feeds with what to expect during the competition that opens Friday and runs through August 11.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"dealers\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"their clients\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"feeds\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The prices of our services will be adjusted due to challenging road traffic conditions and heavy demand,\\\" one seller wrote to customers.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prices\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"our services\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"challenging road traffic conditions\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy demand\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"one seller\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"customers\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swathes of central Paris are blocked off during the festivities, snarling car and pedestrian traffic enough that the Parisian dealer said it would not be worth the trouble, even to see the events.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swathes\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"the festivities\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"car and pedestrian traffic\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parisian dealer\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"the trouble\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one exchange between a seller and customer, seen by AFP, the dealer warns that transactions cannot happen in the open.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9980425246882292, \"rank\": 0.001961314536318221, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one exchange\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"a seller\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"customer\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"the dealer\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"transactions\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"the open\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The police are on the lookout,\\\" the message read.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\":